column6: Ms. Marvel faces one of her toughest challenges yet in a fight against Warren Traveler, half-crazed time traveling former Sorcerer Supreme. Good think Dr. Strange, the current Sorcerer Supreme, decided to stick around!
column8: | penciller (cover):Frank Cho | penciller:Roberto Delatorre | inker:Jimmy Palmiotti | writer:Brian Reed | letterer:Dave Sharpe | colorist:Chris Sotomayor
